The president, Nigeria Labour Congress, Comr. Ayuba Wabba, has commended the  Nigeria Union of Agriculture and Allied Employees for recognising his  contribution Award of Honour during the 2019 Annual Agricultural Development Symposium with theme “Agriculture Mankinds Heritage in Abuja. He stated this yesterday at the event, through his representative, the chairman of Medical and Health Worker, Comrade Shanabo Abubakar. According to the statement, “I receive this award on behalf of the Labour President Comrade Ayuba Waba, and  must say that it is well-deserved. It is commendable that  the President’s contribution to the agricultural sector is being recognised. Also the chairman of the occasion, Alhaji Muhammed Bello Umar, commends the awardee for his outstanding contributions in the country’s agricultural growth.